# Database Migrations

This directory contains Alembic migration scripts for database schema changes.

## Common Commands

### Create a Migration
Generate a new migration script after modifying models.
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "describe_changes"
```

### Apply Migrations
Upgrade to the latest version.
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

Upgrade to a specific revision.
```bash
alembic upgrade <revision_id>
```

### Revert Migrations
Downgrade by one revision.
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

Downgrade to a specific revision.
```bash
alembic downgrade <revision_id>
```

### Stamp Database
Mark the database as being at a specific revision without running migrations.
```bash
alembic stamp <revision_id>
```

Mark as latest (head).
```bash
alembic stamp head
```

### Check Status
Show the current revision of the database.
```bash
alembic current
```

### View History
Show migration history.
```bash
alembic history
```
